name: Baby Samo Coin
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: In October 2021 Baby Samo Coin was born on the Solana blockchain to deliver a new generation of meme powered gains. Our tokenomics work to solve illiquid NFT's by reserving 40% of the total supply to exchange and burn Baby Samo NFT's for the $BABY coin. Half of the Baby Samo NFT mint proceeds go to buy-back and burn $BABY on the open market, creating a positive feedback loop between $BABY and Baby Samo NFT holders.
